10258354229413", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39001705_1110258357562746_522679531656503055_n.png?_nc_cat=107&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=ZTzIw8qi9WMQ7kNvgEMAAi0&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDd53A1sD1A8BdvfMr04iPa-VSwbA4y3BibwBnm8VypQg&oe=6773E7AB"}, "display_name": "Peri-Care Simulator", "keywords": ["CNA", "nursing", "training", "perineal", "healthcare"], "long_description": "The Peri-Care Simulator tutorial immerses Certified Nursing Assistant (CNA) trainees in a virtual environment where they can practice and master the essential techniques for providing proper perineal care. \n\nWith multi-language support (English, Spanish, French, and Arabic), this simulator ensures inclusivity and accessibility for a global audience.  \n\nThe experience is enhanced by an AI companion, acting as a virtual mentor, to answer questions to reinforce learning.\n \n# Key Features: \n- Multi-Language Support: Tailored instructions and narrations in four major languages to cater to diverse learners. \n- AI Companion: An interactive assistant that responds to user queries, and provides clarifications to meet learning needs.(NOTE: Generative AI is still experimental)\n\n# Learning Objectives:\n- Remember the steps and protocols for providing perineal care. \n- Understand the importance of proper hygiene in preventing infections. \n- Apply the correct techniques to provide perineal care safely and respectfully. \n- Analyze the patient's condition and comfort level during the procedure. \n- Evaluate their own technique to ensure it adheres to best practices and safety standards. \n- Create a hygienic and respectful care environment for patients through proper perineal care. \n\nThis thorough approach ensures CNAs are well-prepared to perform perineal care competently and confidently in clinical settings. ", "short_description": "Learn the essential skill of providing perineal care for female patients, ensuring hygiene and comfort with AI guidance and multilingual support for better learning."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://www.holopundits.com/privacy-policy.html", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Holo Pundits", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://www.holopundits.com/", "category": null, "comfort_rating": "COMFORTABLE_FOR_MOST", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "362692211442873", "context_category": "APPS"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "478089301798119"}, {"id": "514087707868786"}, {"id": "1043107547362485"}], "external_subscription_type": "REQUIRED_FOR_SOME_CONTENT", "genres": [], "has_in_app_ads": null, "internet_connection": "REQUIRED", "play_area": "NO_MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en", "ar", "fr", "es_MX"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["STANDING"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "27854633247517569"}, "review_messages": [""]}]}, "cover_square_image": {"uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031407_1112225030688780_5938673640055142895_n.png?stp=dst-png_s360x360&_nc_cat=107&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=xQ9038gr_UsQ7kNvgFURWvp&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAa7ogk1Yf--2Uaj7RrMQzLgznVwTXvp_S1CGv4SjwTNg&oe=6773CCD6"}, "is_concept": false, "is_test": false, "is_trial_offer_valid": false, "display_name": "Peri-Care Simulator", "platform": "ANDROID_6DOF", "context_category": {"context_category": "APPS", "id": "362692211442873"}, "context_topics": [{"topic_name": "Medical", "id": "478089301798119"}, {"topic_name": "Hands-On Training", "id": "514087707868786"}, {"topic_name": "Learning", "id": "1043107547362485"}], "release_date": 1727175420, "lastRevision": {"nodes": [{"id": "26795986606715577", "release_type": "SCHEDULED", "administration_status": "APPROVED", "pdp_